Package antlr4.parser

Class PythonParserBaseListener

java.lang.Object
antlr4.parser.PythonParserBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
PythonParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class PythonParserBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements PythonParserListener
This class provides an empty implementation of PythonParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
